Class Constraint

  • java.lang.Object
    • src.Constraint

  • public class Constraint
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a constraints for the problem. A constraint represents a linear equation. It is composed of entities, their coefficients, a lower bound and an upper bound.
    Author:
    lmarmiesse 6 mars 2013
